    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>演示版会与正式版同步更新！</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经典战斗风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/6474c929d87805d2e58404ea611d0eec.poster.avif?t=1764643565\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/6474c929d87805d2e58404ea611d0eec.webm?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/6474c929d87805d2e58404ea611d0eec.mp4?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你可以使用方向键、基本攻击和分配给每个按键的三个技能。体验带有垂直移动的经典清版动作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于队伍的RPG</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/058814e737e723c37437ae6b0a753981.poster.avif?t=1764643565\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/058814e737e723c37437ae6b0a753981.webm?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/058814e737e723c37437ae6b0a753981.mp4?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>将怪物击飞，击倒，从背后攻击或眩晕它们，以特定技能造成额外伤害。通过用一名队员眩晕怪物并用其他队员造成额外伤害来执行强力的连击攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可选择的9种职业和装备</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/ae8ef21f06ecc3f14e5eb333ba5731dc.poster.avif?t=1764643565\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/ae8ef21f06ecc3f14e5eb333ba5731dc.webm?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/ae8ef21f06ecc3f14e5eb333ba5731dc.mp4?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>从9个职业中选择：战士、圣骑士、锤兵、黑卫士、游侠、巫师、野蛮人、牧师和盗贼。每个角色都可以成为坦克、近战DPS、远程DPS或支持者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色可以通过背景加成、职业加成和装备加成的特殊能力来独特成长。练习并掌握连击，持续造成强力打击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >怪物猎人风格的头目</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/b0073713b92241012f32f57416bc420f.poster.avif?t=1764643565\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/b0073713b92241012f32f57416bc420f.webm?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/b0073713b92241012f32f57416bc420f.mp4?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>特殊怪物大、强大且快速。分析怪物以找到它们的弱点，通过闪避攻击或依赖你的队伍成员的支持来狩猎它们，并使用强力装备和加成。正确的策略将使击败头目及其爪牙变得不再困难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >少量的Roguelite元素</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/73f3ade31b46ee496582cbfc7e2e94fb.poster.avif?t=1764643565\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/73f3ade31b46ee496582cbfc7e2e94fb.webm?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/73f3ade31b46ee496582cbfc7e2e94fb.mp4?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在头目战前清除三个随机阶段。每个清除的阶段都提供各种机会，如招募新队员、增强装备或加强队伍本身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >测试你的独特构建，使用新队员击败头目，并通过已完成任务中解锁的新特性探索新构建。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样化的阶段</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/b5d820b35b520bd4e393efa71ed53494.poster.avif?t=1764643565\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/b5d820b35b520bd4e393efa71ed53494.webm?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/b5d820b35b520bd4e393efa71ed53494.mp4?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >离线双人合作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/d7a886692250a6ad39f75226af19f069.poster.avif?t=1764643565\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/d7a886692250a6ad39f75226af19f069.webm?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/d7a886692250a6ad39f75226af19f069.mp4?t=1764643565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的事件和头目战斗等待着！享受不断吸引玩家的有趣而有价值的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156190/extras/c765b9e2928b750bf563ab54055b3e13.avif?t=1764643565\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p>",
